{% block body %}
    <h1>About OpenSALT</h1>

    <section>
        <p>
            OpenSALT is a tool that allows for managing (importing, creating, editing, exporting) competency frameworks,
            focused on IMS Global's Competency and Academic Standards Exchange (CASE) specification.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Open Source</h2>
